		"description": "<p>At 11th level you gain the ability to use the mindscape to access skills and abilities you might not otherwise possess, or predict attacks with implausible skill. Choose a creature within 60ft of you that you can see. If the target is hostile you gain advantage on the saving throw of any maneuver, spell, or power the target uses against you. If the target is an ally, you may instead use any cantrip, power, or combat maneuver your target knows. This ability lasts for 1 minute, and can be used once per short rest.</p>",
